room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Lock & Clue Escape Rooms in Providence
room_description: Your team of professional thieves has taken on some risky jobs, but this one will push you to the limit. You've been tipped off that a local crime boss has a priceless artifact locked in a vault at a nearby factory. You’ll only have a one hour window to break in and escape with the item. Oh, and if you get caught, you won’t end up in prison, you’ll end up in the morgue. Sounds like a worthy challenge…
